--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Release Note for VIVIECR ver.1.2.1.7 (English version)
Release Date: 2010-Sept-09
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a maintenance release with enhanced functions for VIVIPOS Application (VIVIECR) 1.2.1.x series.
Previous 1.2.1.x releases may be upgraded to this release by installing the XPI file through Add-ons Manager.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This release requires the following applications:
	- VIVIPOS OS Release 1.2.2 or above
	- VIVIPOS App Engine Release 1.2.1.5 or above
	- VIVIPOS WebApp and WebServices Release 1.2.1.2 or above

You should also install appropriate language pack (langpack-en-US_1.2.1.7.xpi) to avoid translation-related issues.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Enhanced Functions
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Ticket#139:
Enhance Table Manager and Layout Manager functions: Only when users switch layout setting to "Compact Table Layout" in Layout Manager, the "Dock Options" tab in Table Manager will show up.

Ticket#142:
Enhance Table Manager function: Automatically recall order to shopping cart when only one order exists in a table.

Ticket#144:
Enhance Rebuild Status function in Table Manager: Remove cache after table status rebuilt, which allows "Rebuild Status" function to take effect immediately without restarting the application.

Ticket#147:
Add one new role for "Return Item" function.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Bugs Fixed
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Ticket#156:	(This bug applies to Taiwan market only)
In the circumstance that when users click "Cash" button twice in a very fast way, the invoice (for Taiwan market) will be printed twice.
This issue has been fixed in 1.2.1.7 release.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

